  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0da2\u0dcf\u0dad\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0d85\u0daf \u0d87\u0dad\u0dca\u0dad\u0dda \u0dbb\u0dcf\u0da2\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0da0\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dba\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Today, instead of democracy, there is state violence",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Opposition leader Mr. Sajith Premadasa said in Colombo that instead of democracy, there is state violence.",
        "The opposition leader also mentioned that the first attack on the democratic struggle of the people of the country was launched on the 9th of May by launching state violence.",
        "He said this while attending a special meeting of the National Reform Movement held at the opposition leader's office in Colombo with the participation of political party leaders, parliamentary public representatives and professionals.",
        "He said that today the state violence is working seriously and instead of a new journey, there is the same old violent journey.",
        "The opposition leader also said that in a situation where a president who became the ruler of the country with a majority of 69 lakhs has been expelled from the country by a public struggle, he cannot do anything arbitrarily.",
        "Mr. Premadasa further said that an appointed dictatorship should not be allowed to practice brutality because of the country's democracy and the rulers should set an example of unity and fairness.",
        "Members of Parliament M. that. Mr. Sumanthiran, Rajitha Senaratne, Tissa Attanayake, P. Digambaram, Harsha de Silva, Dylan Perera, Mujibur Rahman and others were present."
      ],
